sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant W as Widget
  participant API as API
  participant DB as MongoDB
  participant WK as Worker
  participant D as Delivery transport

  W->>API: POST /requests (Idempotency-Key, confirmed:true)
  API->>DB: create_or_replay (unique conversation_id+key) → status received
  API->>DB: enqueue deliver_request job (resource_id = req_)
  API-->>W: {request_id, reference, duplicate}
  WK->>DB: claim job (atomic lease)
  WK->>DB: mark_delivering
  opt retry (attempt > 1)
    WK->>D: find_by_reference (probe — may have already sent)
  end
  WK->>D: deliver (webhook POST / SMTP / simulated)
  alt delivered
    D-->>WK: external reference
    WK->>DB: mark_delivered (+ external_reference)
  else ambiguous / budget exhausted
    WK->>DB: mark_delivery_failed → parked for admin redeliver
  end
